TPM-Scope extends TPMStream by providing:

- TPM SPI transaction reconstruction
- FIFO and CRB transport decoding
- TPM register interpretation
- TPM command and response analysis
- Measured boot analysis
- Interactive desktop and web interfaces

The original TPMStream source code and license are preserved in this repository.
